talk-spotter (2.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add transceiver audio source with Hamlib CAT control via rigctld
  * Add KiwiSDR auto-reconnect with exponential backoff (max_retries,
    retry_delay config options)
  * Add unit tests for grammar, DX cluster, and POTA spotter modules
  * Fix duplicate words in Vosk grammar vocabulary
  * Remove unused imports (PropertyMock, typing.Optional)

