talk-spotter (1.1.2) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add 81 unit tests for command parser
  * Fix Vosk not finalizing words in grammar-constrained mode by force-flushing
    when partial text is stable for 2 seconds
  * Fix unbounded raw_text growth in idle state
  * Switch audio buffer to bytearray for in-place operations
  * Support slash/stroke in callsigns (e.g., VP2E/W1AW, W1AW/VP2/P)
  * Remove redundant keyword highlighting feature

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Fri, 07 Mar 2026 12:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (1.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite command parser: fields can now be spoken in any order
  * Add "callsign" / "call sign" as alternatives to "call"
  * Add "cancel" command to abort without posting
  * Add compound number word support (e.g., "twenty eight" -> 28)
  * Repeated keywords now override earlier attempts (last wins)
  * Idle timeout (10s) replaces fixed deadline from wake phrase
  * Session timeout (60s) hard cap as safety net

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Fri, 07 Mar 2026 02:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (1.0.1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix NATO phonetic X-ray never being detected — Vosk splits "x-ray" into
    two tokens ("x" and "ray") which are now merged before lookup
  * Add "x ray" as a recognized two-word phrase in Vosk grammar

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Thu, 06 Mar 2026 19:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add Vosk grammar constraints for improved command recognition accuracy
  * Remove --spot-mode flag; spotting is now always enabled
  * Add --no-grammar flag to disable vocabulary constraints
  * Add "complete" as an alternative to "end" for finishing commands
  * Fix voice command parsing when entire command is spoken in one utterance
  * Fix premature timeout caused by partial results being fed to command parser
  * Fix frequency not being parsed when spoken in the same utterance as "end"

 -- Evan Boyar <evanboyar@proton.me>  Thu, 06 Mar 2026 12:00:00 -0500

talk-spotter (0.2.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Add POTA spot posting support
  * Add SOTA spot posting support with OAuth authentication
  * Fix RTL-SDR freezing by separating read and process threads
  * Add slow AGC to smooth audio level variations
  * Add DC offset removal to FM demodulator
  * Add second model path option to config
  * Enhance error handling in SOTA authentication

